docs.abstract: For Season 2 of Amazon’s hit show, the director and showrunner Jill Soloway explores family history and introduces new shades into the character of Maura.
docs.snippet: For Season 2 of Amazon’s hit show, the director and showrunner Jill Soloway explores family history and introduces new shades into the character of Maura.
docs.lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES — On the set of “Transparent,” a handful of actors dressed for a flashback scene on a 1930s ocean liner — cloche hats, woolen jackets, long skirts — crowd together on benches in a large wooden container perched atop a gimbal, a device that can simulate the rolling of a ship. Sitting cross-legged on a long table a few yards away, the director Jill Soloway, who created this Amazon series, quietly throws out a few suggestions to the gently swaying actors.

headline.main: In ‘Transparent,’ a Heroine Evolves Further Still

docs.abstract: With a tap on a smartphone, consumers in some areas can have almost anything delivered within hours. But the cost of that is significant, and not always obvious.
docs.snippet: With a tap on a smartphone, consumers in some areas can have almost anything delivered within hours. But the cost of that is significant, and not always obvious.
docs.lead_paragraph: WHEN Emily Yang, a San Francisco tech worker, is running out of cat food, she taps an app called Instacart to order a new bag of kibble to be delivered to her door within hours. For dinner, she often orders through Sprig and Munchery, app-powered services that bring fresh organic meals to her home.

headline.main: The High Price of Delivery App Convenience
headline.print_headline: The High Price of Delivery App Convenience

docs.abstract: The United States is under Nazi and Japanese occupation in this 10-episode alternative-history drama on Amazon Prime.
docs.snippet: The United States is under Nazi and Japanese occupation in this 10-episode alternative-history drama on Amazon Prime.
docs.lead_paragraph: The flag of Nazi-ruled America of 1962 in “The Man in the High Castle” has red and white stripes and a swastika on a field of blue. But even more chilling is how fascism has stamped itself upon American popular culture.

headline.main: Review: ‘The Man in the High Castle’ Imagines America Ruled by 2 Foreign Powers
headline.print_headline: America, One Nation Under Two Flags

docs.abstract: Few would argue that Google knows better than most how to manage huge data centers. But in recent years Amazon has become the leader in selling that expertise to other companies.
docs.snippet: Few would argue that Google knows better than most how to manage huge data centers. But in recent years Amazon has become the leader in selling that expertise to other companies.
docs.lead_paragraph: One of the great mysteries of the tech industry in recent years has been the seeming disinterest of Google, which is now called Alphabet, in competing with Amazon Web Services for corporate customers.

headline.main: Daily Report: Google Gets Serious About Competing in Cloud With Amazon Web Services
